      • calculateProgress

        public double calculateProgress​(@Nonnull
                                Language lang)
        This returns the progress of translation for any given Language. The progress is determined by the amount of translated strings divided by the amount of strings in the english Language file and multiplied by 100.0
        Parameters:
        lang - The Language to get the progress of
        Returns:
        A percentage (0.0 - 100.0) for the progress of translation of that Language
